QuestData.Title: Bad Datas
QuestData.Description: There should be two titan communication devices in this chamber.$b$bIf my translations are correct, one is a death trap and the other will accept the codes and activate the obelisk.$b$bLet's hope I get this right.$b$bLet me know when you're ready.
QuestData.LogDescription: Accompany Harrison Jones in the Chamber of the Moon.
QuestData.RewardText: Okay, $n.$b$bI think I can do this manually, but I'll need your help.
